template5 ${color7}|${offset -9}${voffset -3}^${voffset 3}${tab 50}${color yellow}${upspeedf \1}${tab 2}Kbps\n${alignr}${color0}${upspeedgraph \1 16,150 000000 ffffff}${color7}
